"pierde la asociación actual con los juegos."

#: src/menu/MiiTransformTasksState.cpp:89
msgid ""
"Updates MAC Address and AuthID (WiiU) of the Mii, so that it will apeear as "
"created on this console. Updates Mii Id, so games association is lost."
